I'm going to find Su Muyu.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:14.220
Want to come along?

00:07:15.760 --> 00:07:17.040
- Kites! - Fresh buns!

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.800
- Kites for sale! - Take a look!

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:20.720
Kites in every style!

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:21.480
