But...

00:09:42.790 --> 00:09:44.060
the uncle beside you

00:09:44.080 --> 00:09:45.250
seems keen to stay.

00:09:47.150 --> 00:09:47.730
Muyu,

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.220
we're already here,

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:50.300
so enjoy yourself.

