00:11:36.150 --> 00:11:36.980
Muyu...

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:38.300
Good name!

00:11:38.670 --> 00:11:39.340
A fine name indeed!

00:11:49.870 --> 00:11:51.250
Su Muyu, the Umbrella Ghost?

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.700
