00:11:57.150 --> 00:11:58.310
not the "Umbrella Ghost".

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:01.670
Don't worry.

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:03.340
I'm just here to enjoy the music.

00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:05.300
Ah, Mr. Su...

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.130
