00:36:23.670 --> 00:36:24.940
isn't it?

00:36:27.520 --> 00:36:29.210
Well said.

00:36:29.880 --> 00:36:31.340
I'm almost impressed.

00:36:33.110 --> 00:36:33.570
Speak...

00:36:35.190 --> 00:36:36.130
