00:36:41.960 --> 00:36:42.460
What?

00:36:43.520 --> 00:36:44.650
Do you even know what you're saying?

00:36:46.040 --> 00:36:46.820
Blood River kills anyone,

00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:48.210
